A '''parental collective''' was a unit of socialization among the [[Yuvernian/Legends|Yuvernian]] [[Species/Legends|species]] responsible for the upbringing of the young. Frustrated, [[Cane Adiss/Legends|Cane Adiss's]] parental collective would berate him for turning his mind to traversing [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], rather than the issues of his [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Yuvern/Legends|Yuvern]].

